(2, 'Samsung Galaxy S23', 'samsung-galaxy-s23', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">The Samsung Galaxy S23 will have some big shoes to fill when it arrives next year, given how well Samsung\'s recent flagship phones performed. But we think Samsung is up to the challenge, as it gets the next big phone release ready.</span><br></p>', '<h2 id=\"samsung-galaxy-s23-latest-news-updated-december-13\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 710.4px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both;\">Samsung Galaxy S23 latest news (updated December 13)</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">There could be&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-could-have-big-performance-advantage-over-galaxy-s23\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">three different cooling systems</a>&nbsp;for the three different Galaxy S23 models.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\"><a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-specs-leaked-in-full-ahead-of-launch\" data-original-url=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-ultra-just-got-a-massive-specs-leak\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">A whole bunch of Galaxy S23 Ultra specs</a>&nbsp;just got leaked.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">Our Phones Editor is&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/opinion/im-worried-about-galaxy-s23-will-samsung-repeat-apples-biggest-mistake\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">worried about the Galaxy S23 — could Samsung repeat Apple\'s biggest mistake</a>&nbsp;and focus all the attention on the S23 Ultra this time?</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-just-tipped-to-pull-further-ahead-of-iphone-14-pro-with-video-upgrade\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">Samsung Galaxy S23 range could get a neat 8K video upgrade</a>, which could leave the iPhone 14 Pro phones in the dust.&nbsp;</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">Samsung may stick with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-spec-leak-has-left-us-a-little-disappointed\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">just 8GB of RAM</a>&nbsp;in the basic Galaxy S23 and Galaxy S23 Plus</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">Here\'s a round-up of all the rumored&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-colors\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">Galaxy S23 colors</a>&nbsp;that we\'ve heard about.</li></ul><h2 id=\"samsung-galaxy-s23-possible-release-date\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 710.4px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both;\">Samsung Galaxy S23 possible release date</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">The Galaxy S22 launched in February, so we\'d expect a similar timeline for the Galaxy S23. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/reviews/samsung-galaxy-s21\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">Galaxy S21</a>&nbsp;series came out in January 2021, but Samsung had to make room for the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/reviews/samsung-galaxy-s21-fe\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">Galaxy S21 FE</a>, so it likely pushed back the S22\'s debut. Of course,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/galaxy-s22-fe-reportedly-cancelled-and-its-not-hard-to-understand-why\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">there\'s likely no Galaxy S22 FE in the works</a>&nbsp;at Samsung, so that may not impact the S23 rollout plans.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">If you want evidence that a February 2023 launch is in the cards, a battery for a phone matching the Galaxy S23 Plus\' description showed up for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-release-date-just-tipped-for-february-heres-what-we-know\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">certification with a South Korean agency</a>&nbsp;in early September. The timing matches the S22 rollout, which would seem to suggest a February 2023 launch is on track.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">While one rumor has suggested&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/samsung-galaxy-s23-tipped-to-arrive-sooner-than-expected\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">a mid-January release for the S23</a>, we\'re more confident than ever in a February launch after&nbsp;<a href=\"https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2022/11/28/business/tech/Korea-Samsung-Electronics-Galaxy/20221128180140424.html\" target=\"_blank\" data-url=\"https://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/2022/11/28/business/tech/Korea-Samsung-Electronics-Galaxy/20221128180140424.html\" rel=\"noopener\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">a report from Korea Joongang Daily</a><span class=\"sr-only\" style=\"font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">(opens in new tab)</span>&nbsp;cites Samsung insiders who claim that an Unpacked event is in the works for early February.</p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">What Samsung might include on next year\'s Galaxy S flagship</span><br></p>', 's23.png', 'Smartphones,Samsung', 2, NULL, 3, 'active', '2022-12-16 10:13:23', '2022-12-16 10:13:23'),
(3, 'iPhone 15 — everything we know so far', 'iphone-15-everything-we-know-so-far', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">The iPhone 15 isn\'t expected to debut until September 2023, but there\'s already been a fair number of rumors and leaks for the next iPhones.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">For example, it looks as though Apple will finally embrace USB-C charging and ditch the Lightning port. And we may see an entirely new model dubbed the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-15-ultra\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">iPhone 15 Ultra</a>, which could take the iPhone Pro series to the next level with a super durable titanium design.&nbsp;Of course, we shouldn\'t forget about the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-15-pro\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">iPhone 15 Pro</a>, either.</p>', '<h2 id=\"iphone-15-news-updated-december-9\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 710.4px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both;\">iPhone 15 news (Updated December 9)</h2><ul style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: none; clear: both; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">Even if Apple doesn\'t add USB-C ports to the iPhone 15,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/the-iphone-just-got-an-official-deadline-to-ditch-lightning-for-usb-c\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">it\'ll have to adopt them by 2024</a>.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">One leaker is predicting a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-15-ultra-just-tipped-for-huge-price-hike-this-could-be-a-disaster\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">price hike of up to $200 for the iPhone 15 Ultra</a>&nbsp;over the iPhone 14 Pro Max.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">The iPhone 15 may not get a rounded design after all —&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-15-may-not-get-a-rounded-design-after-all-heres-why\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">here’s why</a>.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">Here\'s our comparison of the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-14-vs-iphone-15\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">iPhone 15 vs. iPhone 14</a>, looking at current leaks so far.</li><li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; list-style: inside none disc;\">An analyst has said that the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/the-iphone-15-might-be-more-of-an-upgrade-that-you-think\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">iPhone 15 could get three significant upgrades including the Dynamic Island</a>.</li></ul><h2 id=\"iphone-15-possible-release-date\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 710.4px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both;\">iPhone 15 possible release date</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">Of all the early iPhone 15 rumors, this is the most set in stone. In the last decade, Apple has only announced its new flagship smartphones outside of September once: October 2020, amid a once-in-a-generation pandemic that necessitated stay-at-home orders and disrupted tech supply chains.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">As such, it is highly likely that the iPhone 15 will arrive in September 2023. Typically Apple announces its phones about ten days before they’re released, with pre-orders opening a week ahead of go-time.</p><h2 id=\"iphone-15-price-speculation\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.7em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-weight: 700; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 30px; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; vertical-align: baseline; width: 710.4px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); clear: both;\">iPhone 15 price speculation</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">With the iPhone 14, there was strong speculation that&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-14-pro-just-tipped-for-a-price-increase-but-theres-some-good-news\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">we would see a 15% price increase</a>, but this turned out to be incorrect — if you live in the United States. Other regions saw a substantial increase, but in the US the only change in pricing was the elimination of the cheapest ‘mini’ model.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">That means that prices currently go from $799 for the 128GB entry-level iPhone 14 all the way up to $1,599 for the 1TB iPhone 14 Pro Max. We would expect something similar this time around, but it’s entirely possible that the iPhone 15 will see the price rise that the US missed out on in 2022. If so, expect an increase of $100 or so.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.5; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\">At least one leaker expects Apple\'s high-end iPhone to see a potentially big price hike over its iPhone 14 predecessor. LeaksApplePro says an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.tomsguide.com/news/iphone-15-ultra-just-tipped-for-huge-price-hike-this-could-be-a-disaster\" data-component-tracked=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(26, 152, 238);\">increase of $100 to $200 could happen for the iPhone 15 Ultra</a>, which could place that model\'s range between $1,199 and $1,299</p>', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;\">All the iPhone 15 and iPhone 15 Pro rumors and leaks in one place</span><br></p>', 'G8UtrXmHcRRXhfZFV8zNcE-1200-80.jpg.webp', 'Smartphones', 2, NULL, 3, 'active', '2022-12-16 10:14:47', '2022-12-16 10:14:47');

